{"tid":325813,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"因為屋企問題 長期精神狀況欠佳","createTime":"2017-07-17T13:07:13.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-22T14:18:42.000Z","uid":119023,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"9dd54995ac938a496627655596e26ae8e1a986f5","tid":325813,"uid":119023,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-17T13:07:13.000Z","msg":"上年睇醫生話我有dsythimia  <br />\n唔係抑鬱 係比抑鬱症好少少的一個病<br />\n原因一匹布咁長 <br />\n學業 問題<br />\n不過而家諗深一層 其中一部分係屋企長期ge問題搞到我咁<br />\n食左藥一年 而家停左藥 <br />\n感覺食藥個期好番好多<br />\n而家又差番<br />\n<br />\n出呢個post係想問 <br />\n如果知道呢個病係關家庭事<br />\n係咪應該遠離一下屋企？<br />\n我可以點幫自己<br />\n<br />\n利申 單親 21歲<br />\n長期同屋企溝通唔到 爸爸好stubborn <br />\n唔係三言兩語可以講清楚<br />\n之前試過個半月唔係屋企 去exchange <br />\n居然開心番好多 但一番到黎又衰過"},{"pid":"127037f9c526527e791cef0fbd3046553f4c9d64","tid":325813,"uid":73748,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-17T13:10:35.000Z","msg":"搬出黎"},{"pid":"096abe275dbf314a66b761de4daef273feb1b77e","tid":325813,"uid":55511,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-17T13:11:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>搬出黎</blockquote><br />\n正解"},{"pid":"6d239b36a8fcbe0685ac3b2a98f68e5cf4197c8c","tid":325813,"uid":121546,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-17T13:12:19.000Z","msg":"有冇聽到把聲叫你殺哂D屋企人?"},{"pid":"58f0e6121cf3574aaf0657b5020dcb7c540d43b4","tid":325813,"uid":73748,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-17T13:13:58.000Z","msg":"你屋企得你同你阿爸？"},{"pid":"ba4d9a24542d79684b97ba33356cb37bbc5fd392","tid":325813,"uid":119023,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-17T13:13:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有冇聽到把聲叫你殺哂D屋企人?</blockquote><br />\n冇 我唔想殺哂d屋企人<br />\n我唔憎佢地"},{"pid":"fa9f962c06109ff88295eaf046c7009d9c2a4552","tid":325813,"uid":25327,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-17T13:16:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>有冇聽到把聲叫你殺哂D屋企人?</blockquote><br />\n冇 我唔想殺哂d屋企人<br />\n我唔憎佢地</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n殺曬佢地咪冇家庭囉